'''Julian Tolkien''', son of [[Hilary Tolkien]], is the nephew of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]. He and his wife Glynis have three sons: [[Tim Tolkien|Timothy]], Nicholas and Stephen.

Julian Tolkien has recalled that his uncle John Ronald was a "''witty raconteur''" and that he "''saw the fun in things and had strong Christian principles''".<ref>Sandra Carter, "[https://www.thisislocallondon.co.uk/news/307760.related-to-tolkien/ Related to Tolkien]" (dated 14 December 2001) at [https://www.thisislocallondon.co.uk/ This is Local London] (accessed 21 April 2024)</ref>
